Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.84,0:00:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我和麻郁先生说了真相后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生找了一整晚深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.63,0:00:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,回来时说到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我能够刺痛般地感受到 这只是逞强而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 哥哥也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,担心深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,请…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(560,455)\fs40\fn华康少女字体\3c&Hcdabff\bord2}3个人的双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要老让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,随随便便地离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,却又悠闲地出现在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,(沉默)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,脸那么红
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,向神城君告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,用不着这么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是时机太糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她在竭斯底里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有恋爱的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,结果深衣奈那家伙到回家都不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那理由是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子是难懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙说的和做的不同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,暂住在同班同学的晴子家里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,同班同学的四道晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.73,0:05:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有个特别的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让哥哥好好来关心你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把她带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,想像什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我去见深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉的女孩子间更好些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,突然跑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,像是多了个姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,像是多了个妹妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,打个比方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,打个比方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时让我住一下可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是OK的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就当作是自己的房间嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,随便些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会这样认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不…礼节还是要遵守的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,又有朋友来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹有3个了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧 桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥只是说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我把换洗的衣服拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谈一谈好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说赤裸相见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 深衣奈小姐说重要事情的时候多数在浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是麻郁听不见的秘密房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,相当精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为你还在垂头丧气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我有垂头丧气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是知道了是麻郁的亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也觉得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而且深衣奈小姐离家出走时也注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢麻郁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想3个人在一起多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,3个人在一起好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想3人一起在那个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要离家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐如果是当真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会来晴子家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会到更远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,留在家里也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说喜欢麻郁先生也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明明可以告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,却不和麻郁先生说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也许有这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不仅是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,同盟协约第3条还有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亲人的一方要支持和麻郁先生…和麻郁先生的恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可是桦恋你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我不希望麻郁先生的恋人不是深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 回家还要等一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没法看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没法看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,知道麻郁是外人后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,无法直视麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一说话 心里就砰砰跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,变成这样 简直无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…除了麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果…如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,两人都那么坚强 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,象老婆婆一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你…会发生不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子危机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,椿 一个人太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他是谁…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈…还是劝不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她说再过些日子就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,知道在哪里也就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个废墟里竟然留着我们的记录啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么看都不象20年以上没人住的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,从妈妈的笔记来看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们3人一起住的地方就是这个房子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的家就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.17,0:11:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,即使看了那本日记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道妈妈在哪里是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是个线索
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋希望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以去找妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我…什么也不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也觉得这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不在意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,说不在意是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我和麻郁先生…不 是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,和深衣奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,3人一起住在这个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的“现在”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是深衣奈不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,当她知道了和我们没有血缘关系的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就制造了距离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明明无论是亲人还是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,都无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐不是在烦恼这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈小姐正视着“现在”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈的“现在” 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那…从我的嘴里说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 请相信她 深衣奈小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,即使知道了我和桦恋是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也没有实在的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,照我来看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋和深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两人才象双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,即使没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我和深衣奈小姐也是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,深…深…深衣奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈说要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也不听劝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,发觉时已经不在家里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,神城君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看见深衣奈了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我也正想告诉你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤同学向海之口走去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想到哪里去？ 深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是太奇怪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在意自己是外人的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得会被赶出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这么心胸狭窄的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,即使没有血缘 即使是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也能成为家属
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们结婚就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,离家出走这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是求婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是…是假设…这是假设的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好高兴 好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:14:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么可怕的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想在那个家里 想到要命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 怕什么时候会和麻郁产生隔阂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能住在那个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能住在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你太在意将来的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不考虑现在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会有将来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,想和麻郁在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想和麻郁 桦恋一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,住在那个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你 从那开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看了好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,神城真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可以确定是留校察看处分了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老师就当作没看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,岛崎 先辈 会长 连老师也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老师是帮恋爱少女那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不成为理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要问我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是被晴子叫到这里来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,完全被识破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大家回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,痛 好痛 麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么就对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不能对对先辈和老师出手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你做代表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,椿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,康生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,老师就当作没看见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,神城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,康生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子也想谈恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,晴子的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是个真正的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.86,0:18:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真过分 桦恋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,协助恋爱 没有做到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是首先麻郁先生是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我跟哥哥撒撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是妹妹哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和最喜欢的哥哥勾着手有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁 今晚想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 一副新婚妻子的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁只是我一个人的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的麻郁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要无视我的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:18:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,麻郁怎么想呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那个家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的家 住在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不过有麻郁的风范
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想从今以后也会有许许多多事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在我们回到那个家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,三人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不断地重复着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成为家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,深衣奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩子时的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是我和你
